{
  "stem": "5644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From our opposition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two boys to take them out of there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us their secret name, their secret there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a secret word, and we get out with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we start to walk with him together, to the next house what I brought him in, Karski.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now there's a very important thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How Karski knew, after so many years, that David was the one, or David know Karski was the one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's very important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came to a home, he got his, his talk with the-- with the leaders.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then-- we didn't, we haven't been, when they talk between.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was actually asked by the Polish underground that the Jews want him, because before he's going overseas on a mission to England and America, to, to try to give a message from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is your own will, because I spoke to Karski.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of his own free will.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is on your own will.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you'd like to go into the ghetto, we'll let you in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll let you go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They will arrange it, we'll let you go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you don't want it, you can refuse it. because it's risky.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he chose to go into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very good-- look, he-- to me, he's absolutely God.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What he did for us, nobody would do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came in there, and, as exactly, he was dressed like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came in, and went up there, and this is the most important few things which happened there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, I saw him at the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he seen two boys, German shooting to a window, and killing some people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he nearly collapsed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
